freeCodeCamp - HTML & HTML5 

Basics

INICIO: Todos los documentos empiezan con <!DOCTYPE html> ......   
											<html> 
												<head>
													<link, meta, title, and style>
												</head>
												<body>
													<h1 h2 p form etc>
												</body> 
											</html>

COMMENTS: <!--   -->

IMAGES: <img src="https://www.freecatphotoapp.com/your-image.jpg">

LINK A EXTERNO (anchor): 	<a href="https://freecodecamp.org">this links to freecodecamp.org</a>

	Nest anchor con paragraph				<p>
  												Here's a <a target="_blank" href="http://freecodecamp.org"> link to freecodecamp.org</a> for you to follow.
											</p>

LINK A INTERNO: (misma pagina) <a href="#footer">Footer</a> 
								<h2 id="footer">Footer</h2>

PHOTO A LINK: <a href="#"><img src="https://bit.ly/fcc-running-cats" alt="Three kittens running towards the camera."></a>



UNORDERED LIST: <ul>
  					<li>milk</li>
  					<li>cheese</li>
				</ul>

ORDERED LIST: 	<ol>
 				 <li>Garfield</li>
 				 <li>Sylvester</li>
			 	</ol>

FIELD TEXT (input): <input type="text" placeholder="Escribe aqui">

FORM TO SUBMIT DATA: 	<form action="https://url-where-you-want-to-submit-form-data">
							<input type="text" placeholder="Escribe aqui">
							<button type="submit">this button submits the form</button>
						</form>

REQUIRED: <input type="text" required>

RADIO: 

		LABELS:   	<label for="outdoor"> 
  						<input id="outdoor" value="outdoor" type="radio" name="indoor-outdoor" checked >outdoor 
					</label>
					<label for="indoor"> 
  						<input id="indoor" value="indoor" type="radio" name="indoor-outdoor">indoor 
					</label>	

		CHECKBOXES: <label for="loving">
						<input id="loving" type="checkbox" name="personality"> Loving
					</label>

NEST MANY ELEMENTS: division element <div>   </div>
